cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the integration of symbolic reasoning and deep learning, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper specifically focuses on autoencoders, which are commonly used in computer vision and image processing, and proposes a method for injecting a symbolic generative framework onto the feature layer. Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.CV, followed by cs.CL and cs.NE.
